              <p>yeah I think we need to review the generator.... <br><a class="mention" href="/users/johannes">@johannes</a>, how about following one of these <br><a href="http://static.usenix.org/event/usenix99/full_papers/deraadt/deraadt_html/node17.html" class="onebox" target="_blank">http://static.usenix.org/event/usenix99/full_papers/deraadt/deraadt_html/node17.html</a><br><a href="http://preshing.com/20121224/how-to-generate-a-sequence-of-unique-random-integers/" class="onebox" target="_blank">http://preshing.com/20121224/how-to-generate-a-sequence-of-unique-random-integers/</a></p>

